# Trivy release-image vulnerability allowlist.
#
# The default is intentionally empty. Add one CVE or GHSA identifier per line
# only after documenting the affected package, why remediation is not currently
# possible, the approving maintainer, and an expiry/review date in adjacent
# comments. Trivy still fails tag builds on every unlisted HIGH or CRITICAL
# finding.
#
# Example (do not copy without a real review):
# CVE-2099-0001  # package=x reason="no fixed version" owner=@maintainer expires=2099-02-01
